/*
	This folder should *not* contain a directory named ngpl, which
	contains code that is not covered by the GPL licence and is
	only available in the form of compiled binaries.

	If this directory does contain ngpl, you should delete it
	and compile the GPL-conforming library, libcmatrix_gpl.a
	The pNMRsim simulation package, however, can only be linked
	against the full library, libcmatrix.a
*/
